      <block layout="text-right">
        <text>
          <p>The "Black Column Marble Gambler" is an object built from old relays and components salvaged from an ancient telex machine.</p>
          <p>Try to guess through which hole the marble is swept.</p>
          <p>A lift transports the marble to a rotating disk on the top, where a Smurf will try to sweep the marble into one of the gates.</p>
          <p>Your reward when you guessed right? A bright electronic smile!</p>
